类 Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.Tile
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Comparable<Tile>

    public class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Tile>
    A class representing a tile.
    版本:
    0.2 11/14/2014 1) Change the data from int to char;, 0.1 11/14/2014
    作者:
    Dawei Fan

    • 字段概要

      字段 
      限定符和类型 字段和说明
      int area
      Total area of a tile, bigger tiles should be tried first in the main search routine to reduce complexity.
      char[][] data
      2-D array of core data of a tile, in which 0 represents empty and positive numbers represent block.
      int l
      Width and length of a tile, Eg: 1 0 2 1 1 0 w = 3, l = 2
      java.util.List<char[][]> sfpattern
      A list of all possible available patterns with spin and flip, including 1, 2, or 4 patterns.
      java.util.List<char[][]> spattern
      A list of all possible available patterns with spin, including 1, 2, or 4 patterns.
      int spin
      The spin of a tile with 0, 1, 3 which means it has 1, 2, 4 available directions.
      int w
      Width and length of a tile, Eg: 1 0 2 1 1 0 w = 3, l = 2

    • 字段详细资料

      • data

        public char[][] data
        2-D array of core data of a tile, in which 0 represents empty and positive numbers represent block. Different positive numbers represent different colors.

      • spattern

        public java.util.List<char[][]> spattern
        A list of all possible available patterns with spin, including 1, 2, or 4 patterns.

      • sfpattern

        public java.util.List<char[][]> sfpattern
        A list of all possible available patterns with spin and flip, including 1, 2, or 4 patterns.

      • w

        public int w
        Width and length of a tile, Eg:

        1 0

        2 1

        1 0

        w = 3, l = 2

      • l

        public int l
        Width and length of a tile, Eg:

        1 0

        2 1

        1 0

        w = 3, l = 2

      • spin

        public int spin
        The spin of a tile with 0, 1, 3 which means it has 1, 2, 4 available directions.

      • area

        public int area
        Total area of a tile, bigger tiles should be tried first in the main search routine to reduce complexity.
